DESCRIPTION:
xBuildSite is a GUI frontend to 'xataface' used to greate frontend's to mysql
and mssql databases.

INSTALLATION:
Unpack the .zip file to te 'htdocs' directory of your httpd server.
'xbSettings.php' may need some editing since this file is used to indicate the
placement of xataface.

DEVELOPMENT AND TESTING PLATFORM:
I am using a win7 machine with 'xampp' (installed in 'c:/xampp') and xataface
placed in 'c:/xampp/htdocs/xataface'. xBuiltsite is placed in
'c:/xampp/htdocs/xBuildSite'.
